h2. About

Simple personlab website CMS base on Ruby on Rails

h2. Demo

 * "Front":http://personlab.heroku.com/ 
 * "Admin":http://personlab.heroku.com/cpanel   (user:admin password:123123)

h2. Features 

* Weblog,Single page system.
* auto sync Twitter message show on Homepage.
* auto show recent Google Reader share entry on Share page.
* custom About with HTML at Admin panel.
* Textile with Signle page body format.

h2. Install & Configure

h3. Install on Ubuntu
* $ sudo sh install.sh
